videos.description: Kihei Clark attempts to throw an alley-oop to Jay Huff, but the ball instead goes directly into the basket for a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Virginia accidentally hits 3 on alley-oop attempt) 2020/02/19

videos.headline: Virginia accidentally hits 3 on alley-oop attempt

videos.description: Virginia executes the pick-and-roll as Braxton Key feeds a rolling Mamadi Diakite for the powerful two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Diakite rocks the rim for Virginia) 2020/02/19

videos.headline: Diakite rocks the rim for Virginia

videos.description: With the clock winding down in the first half, Jay Huff connects on a 3-pointer from the top of the key to give Virginia a 12-point halftime lead.
videos.headline: Huff's triple beats 1st-half buzzer

videos.description: Boston College's Jarius Hamilton knocks down a 3-pointer and Virginia's Kody Stattmann answers on the other end with a 3 of his own.
videos.headline: Boston College, Virginia trade treys

videos.description: Virginia's Kihei Clark tosses a lob to Jay Huff, who catches the ball with his left hand and contorts midair to convert the alley-oop layup.
videos.headline: Huff adjusts for acrobatic alley-oop
